                    [li]Phantasm - A phantasm spell creates a mental image that usually only the caster and the subject (or subjects) of the spell can perceive. This impression is totally in the minds of the subjects. It is a personalized mental impression, all in their heads and not a fake picture or something that they actually see. Third parties viewing or studying the scene donâ€™t notice the phantasm. All phantasms are mind-affecting spells.[/li]
